{
  "stem": "27443.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She cut off a piece from my dress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In fact, just before we were liberated, both of us got our period back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from a piece from her shirt, she got a long shirt, she made like a napkin holder.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like a belt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To hold pieces for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I was finished, she started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we both alternated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, I went towards a train to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I still lived with a dream that when I come back to my hometown, that I would find somebody from my family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to my hometown, and I went back to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I came off the train, I met a friend of my mother's that arrived there before me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he recognized me, and he already had an apartment with other few boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he took me and my girlfriend to his-- to their apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I came there, and that man was from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had formed a [NON-ENGLISH] for the Jews, that every morning, by [NON-ENGLISH], they posted a big list.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whoever was liberated posted their name, that we should be able to see if we find somebody from the families.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And every morning, my girlfriend and I, we went to the [NON-ENGLISH] to see if anybody became liberated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At one point, I received a letter in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I received a letter from Skarzysko, from David's brother, Moshe, who lives now in Haifa, telling me that I should please come to Skarzysko by train, because he heard news that David is alive.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I left my girlfriend [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Lodz, and I told her, you stay put.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
